	(text "Power Supply\n\n12-24V DC input (barrel jack + Phoenix COMBICON)\n  → SS14 reverse polarity diode\n  → TVS overvoltage clamp\n  → 56µF 63V bulk cap\n  → TPS54202DDCR sync buck → 5V rail\n    (4.7µH inductor, 100k/22.1k FB divider)\n    → TCAN1044V, OLED carrier\n    → LM1117IMP-3.3 LDO → 3.3V rail\n      → ESP32-S3-MINI (~300mA peak)\n      → STM32G0B1 (~20mA)\n      → ADM3260 VDD1 (~10mA)\n\nADM3260 isoPower → ISO_3V3 (isolated)\n  → ADS1115, OPA2376, bias divider (~1.3mA total)"
